---
import LegalLayout from "../layouts/LegalLayout.astro";
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Data Deletion — OCCULTA"
  description="How to request deletion of personal data held by OCCULTA."
>
  <h1>Data Deletion Instructions</h1>
  <p class="last-updated"><strong>Last updated</strong>: 2026-05-14</p>

  <p>
    OCCULTA Marketing Intelligence ("OCCULTA") processes marketing data on behalf of business clients. If you wish to request deletion of personal data associated with you, follow the steps below.
  </p>

  <h2>If you are an authorised user of a Tenant</h2>
  <p>
    Contact your Tenant administrator. They control your account within the Service and can revoke your access and trigger deletion.
  </p>

  <h2>If you are a Tenant or otherwise unable to use the in-app flow</h2>
  <p>Send an email to <strong>support@occulta.co</strong> with:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Subject: "Data Deletion Request"</li>
    <li>The email address associated with your account</li>
    <li>The Tenant name (if applicable)</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We will:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>Acknowledge within 5 business days</li>
    <li>Verify your identity</li>
    <li>Delete your personal data within 30 days, except where retention is required by law (e.g. tax records, audit logs subject to legal hold)</li>
    <li>Confirm completion in writing</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Data we delete</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Account and authentication records</li>
    <li>Audit log entries identifying you</li>
    <li>Cached AI responses linked to your queries</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data we may retain</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Aggregated, non-identifying marketing metrics (these contain no personal data)</li>
    <li>Records required by Portuguese fiscal law (10 years)</li>
    <li>Records under active legal hold</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Meta Platform users</h2>
  <p>If you wish to remove OCCULTA's access to your Meta data and trigger deletion:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>Go to Facebook Settings → Apps and Websites, or Instagram Settings → Apps and Websites, or Meta Business Manager → Business Settings → Integrations</li>
    <li>Remove "OCCULTA Marketing Intelligence" from the list of connected apps or partners</li>
    <li>Tokens are revoked automatically by Meta at this point</li>
    <li>OCCULTA purges associated data within 90 days of token revocation</li>
  </ol>
  <p>
    You may additionally email support@occulta.co to request immediate deletion rather than waiting for the 90-day cycle.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>support@occulta.co</p>
</LegalLayout>
